&lt;li&gt;Structure and negotiate holistic multi-currency deals that bundle MCS and Currency Conversion, pricing across both products to deliver merchant value while capturing the full multi-currency management relationship for Stripe&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage C-suite and treasury stakeholders—including CFOs, Treasurers, and Engineering leaders—to articulate Stripe&#39;s multi-currency value proposition and displace competitors managing FX flows off-platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the FX and multi-currency GTM product specialist for the broader Account Executive team, partnering on complex deals and helping build repeatable sales motions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and execute go-to-market strategies for new product segments, including pitch frameworks, displacement playbooks, and bundled pricing approaches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with product, treasury, and core account teams to support merchant activation, resolve deal blockers, and feed market intelligence back into product development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
